data.description: Here’s your chance to own this Beautifully Refreshed SFH in a Well Desired Community! Features 4 bedrooms and 3 Full bathrooms! Open layout, new carpet & freshly painted. The Upper level has a spacious living room, separate dining room that’s open to the kitchen and 3 well appointed bedrooms including the Primary Bedroom with an en-suite bathroom. The Finished lower level features a cozy fireplace and spacious open recreation room along with the 4th bedroom and a full bathroom; this is the perfect In-Law Suite or Guest Quarters! The Spruced up exterior features a large deck that overlooks the sprawling fenced-in backyard; perfect for entertaining! Parking is a breeze with your private driveway. Nothing to do here but move in and enjoy. Welcome Home!
